dc_title_s: Map of the city of Ann Arbor, Michigan showing University of Michigan public buildings, schools and factories; revised, enlarged and copyrighted Sept. 1907 by Harold D. Gould, publisher.
dc_description_s: Includes key to buildings. "Ann Arbor plant, the Richmond & Backus Co., Printers." 1 map: 40 x 36 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
